        <!-- Body -->
        <div class="essay-body">

            <p>Every organization tells itself a story about who matters most. The CEO who makes the call. The founder who ships the product. The strategist who produces the insight. These are hero roles — the ones that carry prestige, that get profiled, that justify the title.</p>

            <!-- Margin annotation: OpenAI's context architecture -->
